In [41]:
senate30_counts = senate30.groupby(['zipcode', 'month']).size().reset_index(name='counts')
senate30_counts = senate30_counts.set_index(['zipcode', 'month']).sort_index()

senate30_counts['pct_change'] = senate30_counts.groupby(level = 0).counts.apply(lambda x: x.pct_change()).to_numpy()
senate30_counts.reset_index().pivot('month', 'zipcode', 'pct_change').plot(figsize=(20,20))
